cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper deals with sentiment mining, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves the use of machine learning classifiers, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The evaluation methods used in the paper involve sampling techniques, which is related to cs.CY (Computers and Society). Finally, the paper deals with online product reviews, which is related to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
